{
  "title": "Magrathea ObjectStore — 用户手册",
  "lang": "cn",
  "document": {
    "type": "document",
    "title": "Magrathea ObjectStore — 用户手册",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "section",
        "id": "_前端概述",
        "title": "前端概述",
        "level": 1,
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "html": "Magrathea ObjectStore 包含一个基于 Vue.js 的管理前端，运行在 8081 端口。"
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "id": "_访问前端",
            "title": "访问前端",
            "level": 2,
            "blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "在浏览器中打开："
              },
              {
                "type": "list",
                "style": "ulist",
                "items": [
                  {
                    "text": "<code><a href=\"http://localhost:8081/\" class=\"bare\">http://localhost:8081/</a></code> — 默认",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<code><a href=\"http://&lt;host&gt;:8081/\" class=\"bare\">http://&lt;host&gt;:8081/</a></code> — 从局域网的其他机器",
                    "blocks": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "前端由管理服务器（独立的嵌入式 Netty，端口 8081）提供，独立于端口 8080 上的 S3 API。"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "id": "_页面",
            "title": "页面",
            "level": 2,
            "blocks": [
              {
                "type": "table",
                "headers": [
                  "页面",
                  "URL",
                  "描述"
                ],
                "rows": [
                  [
                    "仪表盘",
                    "<code>/</code>",
                    "玻璃拟态设计概览"
                  ],
                  [
                    "存储桶",
                    "<code>/buckets</code>",
                    "S3 存储桶管理"
                  ],
                  [
                    "存储策略",
                    "<code>/storage-policies</code>",
                    "存储策略配置（管理 API）"
                  ],
                  [
                    "文档",
                    "<code>/docs</code>",
                    "本用户手册"
                  ]
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "id": "_语言支持",
            "title": "语言支持",
            "level": 2,
            "blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "前端通过 vue-i18n 支持 5 种语言："
              },
              {
                "type": "list",
                "style": "ulist",
                "items": [
                  {
                    "text": "English (en)",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Italiano (it)",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Español (es)",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Deutsch (de)",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "中文 (cn)",
                    "blocks": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "可以通过右上角的语言选择器切换语言。"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "id": "_主题",
            "title": "主题",
            "level": 2,
            "blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "界面采用玻璃拟态设计："
              },
              {
                "type": "list",
                "style": "ulist",
                "items": [
                  {
                    "text": "磨砂玻璃背景 (<code>backdrop-filter: blur</code>)",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "渐变覆盖层",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "平滑过渡",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "深色主题与强调色",
                    "blocks": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "id": "_管理_api",
            "title": "管理 API",
            "level": 2,
            "blocks": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "管理 API 采用 REST 风格并支持 HATEOAS，在端口 8081 上可用："
              },
              {
                "type": "list",
                "style": "ulist",
                "items": [
                  {
                    "text": "<code>GET /admin/health</code> — 健康检查",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<code>GET /admin/storage-policies</code> — 列出所有存储策略",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<code>GET /admin/storage-policies/{id}</code> — 获取单个策略",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<code>POST /admin/storage-policies</code> — 创建策略",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<code>PUT /admin/storage-policies/{id}</code> — 更新策略",
                    "blocks": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<code>DELETE /admin/storage-policies/{id}</code> — 删除策略",
                    "blocks": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "html": "所有响应均包含用于 HATEOAS 导航的 <code>_links</code>。"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}